BEGIN:VEVENT
CATEGORIES:Women's Herstory Month
DESCRIPTION:Choosing a major or career isn’t just about job prospects—it’s 
 about what excites you! In this talk\, we’ll explore how hobbies can influe
 nce STEM pathways\, and spark ideas. From tinkering and crafting to coding 
 and experimenting\, I’ll share how personal interests have fueled my projec
 ts and papers\, and how you can turn what you love into what you do. Expect
  stories\, laughs\, and a fresh perspective on why your passions matter in 
 STEM. Please register to attend this hybrid event.
DTEND:20260311T184500Z
DTSTAMP:20260311T170247Z
DTSTART:20260311T173000Z
GEO:42.020943;-87.749884
LOCATION:Skokie Campus\, C120
