BEGIN:VEVENT
CATEGORIES:TRIO,Academic Success and Beyond Workshops
DESCRIPTION:The financial literacy workshops aim to inform TRIO students of
  the financial aid process within a college/university setting. Students wi
 ll have an opportunity to learn about the various types of financial aid av
 ailable. These workshops will prepare students to prepare\, complete\, and/
 or renew their FAFSA\, learn how to budget their finances and build their p
 ersonal credit.\n\n \n\nTRIO will aim to educate students on making financi
 al decisions that will help them throughout their college careers and in th
 eir personal lives. In conjunction with the workshops\, TRIO will introduce
  GradReady to TRIO students and provide topics for review on personal finan
 ces\, loans\, and budgeting.
DTEND:20260312T193000Z
DTSTAMP:20260311T170247Z
DTSTART:20260312T180000Z
