 mportant Reminder: this is an optional event and does not fulfill ARW requi
 rements. If you plan to complete placement testing that day\, you must sche
 dule a testing appointment in advance through the website.\n\n\nPlease regi
 ster to confirm your attendance.\n\n\nFor questions\, please contact the Of
 fice of Admission at admission@oakton.edu or 847.635.1700.
