 le to perform two stirring romantic pieces: the Adagietto from Gustav Mahle
 r’s 5th Symphony\, and Five Variants of Dives and Lazarus by Ralph Vaugh Wi
 lliams. This unique concert\, directed by Daniel Golden\, will also include
  film music by John Williams and Alexandre Desplat as well as David Bowie s
 ongs.\n\n \n\nTickets and purchasing options:\n\n$8 general admission\; $6 
 students and seniors.\n\nTickets are available for purchase at the Box Offi
